.TH "zpa2326_sample_oneshot" 9 "zpa2326_sample_oneshot" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
zpa2326_sample_oneshot \- Perform a complete one shot sampling cycle.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" zpa2326_sample_oneshot
.BI "(struct iio_dev *indio_dev "  ","
.BI "enum iio_chan_type type "  ","
.BI "int *value "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "indio_dev" 12
The IIO device associated with the sampling hardware.
.IP "type" 12
Type of measurement / channel to fetch from.
.IP "value" 12
Sample output.
.SH "RETURN"
Zero when successful, a negative error code otherwise.
